channel.title: Please help asap!
channel.description: Hello, I am having problems compiling clients with the signlink class. EVERY client I have attempted to compile has fail do to errors related to signlink. Every client has the signlink class, the class is imported in all the other classes that use it, the name of the class correctly spelled and everything. I've tried to compile about thirty clients so far and it's the same shit. Does anyone have any advice? My skype is: christopher.rosean Thank you in advance. :)
